FIG. 5 provides a partial enlarged view of the holder in accordance with preferred embodiments of the present invention, and illustrates a second embodiment of the deformable strip used as a retaining mechanism;


FIGS. 6 and 7 illustrate an alternative embodiment of the present invention, in which coupling members are provided to enable a number of holders to be attached to one another; and


FIGS. 8 and 9 illustrate the holder of preferred embodiments of the present invention with a CD partially and fully inserted, respectively.
